snippet.title: Dark Lord trailer
snippet.description:
Unleash your power in Dark Lord, a card-based roguelike RPG filled with strategy, adventure, and sardonic wit. Rule your growing realm with an iron fist, fortify the stronghold, and avoid getting stabbed in the back by your advisors!

Learn more and add to wishlist:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2515030/Dark_Lord

Join our Discord server to stay tuned:
https://discord.gg/DT68NpcwJm
